item.value: String collect = songIds.stream().map(String::valueOf).collect(Collectors.joining(",")); JSONObject obj = restTemplate.getForEntity("song/url?id={1}", JSONObject.class, collect).getBody(); Assert.notNull(obj, "get song url response body is null"); if (Objects.equals(obj.getInteger(Constant.NODEAPI_CODE_KEY), Constant.NODEAPI_SUCCESS_CODE)) { List<Map> data = obj.getJSONArray("data").toJavaList(Map.class); if (!CollectionUtils.isEmpty(data)) { List<Pair<Long, String>> songUrls = new ArrayList<>(); data.forEach(o -> { Long id = Long.valueOf((Integer) o.get("id")); String url = (String) o.get("url"); songUrls.add(Pair.of(id, url)); }); return songUrls; } }
